{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01LvwzJ8stmSXZDiRkpFmHjA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The ConfigMap `change-plan` is created with 314 lines of `plan.md`. The live cluster is unchanged — both deployments still running, the completed job pod intact.\n\nHere's a summary of what the plan covers:\n\n**6 gaps identified (cross-referenced with the existing `config-audit` ConfigMap):**\n\n| # | Gap | Risk |\n|---|---|---|\n| 1 | **RBAC** — Role grants `delete` on pods; tighten to minimum verbs | Low |\n| 2 | **Image** — Mutable `3.5.3` tag; pin to `sha256` digest | Low-Med |\n| 3 | **Security contexts** — No `runAsNonRoot`, no capability drop on any workload; add UID 185 + `allowPrivilegeEscalation: false` | Medium |\n| 4 | **Network policies** — No policies at all; add default-deny + explicit allow for ports 7077/8080/8081 | Med-High |\n| 5 | **Job config** — `--master local[2]` bypasses the deployed cluster; switch to `spark://spark-master:7077` | Low |\n| 6 | **Capacity** — Single worker replica; scale to 2 for fault tolerance | Low |\n\nEach step in the plan includes the exact YAML/command to apply, a verification block with expected output, and a rollback procedure. The plan also includes a pre-change backup step and a post-upgrade checklist."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":707,"cache_read_input_tokens":45089,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":707},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7ed9bf79-e2dd-4c8c-a459-ba0f89715c35","uuid":"a77d6a1b-fc8a-4081-8f4d-1046767f2417","request_id":"req_011Cc6ko9eAxxRxZVqSbc6C5"}
